"{\"uid\": \"thedrum.com-news-autodesk-lead-1bn-green-infrastructure-plan-the-la-2028-olympics-paralympics\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Advertisement  August 6, 2024|3 min read  Listen to article4 min  Over the next four years, Autodesk's software will support LA28's \\\"no-new-permanent-venues\\\" plan, which will adapt existing infrastructure and build temporary facilities throughout Los Angeles.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 259, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 92, \"end\": 100, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Autodesk\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.40859526228561e-16, \"text\": \"Autodesk\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Autodesk\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Autodesk\"}, {\"begin\": 247, \"end\": 258, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\", \"score\": 0.9999999410297296, \"rank\": 5.379534885379965e-08, \"text\": \"Los Angeles\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Autodesk Official Design Platform to Support Sustainable Games Infrastructure  Autodesk, a leading software provider for architecture, engineering, design and construction, has been appointed the \\\"Official Design and Make Platform\\\" for the Los Angeles 2028 Olympic and Paralympic Games (LA28).\", \"from\": 261, \"to\": 554, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 501, \"end\": 517, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2028_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Los Angeles 2028\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2028_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2028_Summer_Olympics\"}, {\"begin\": 530, \"end\": 546, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paralympic_Games\", \"score\": 0.9999989151407562, \"rank\": 7.119932940958844e-07, \"text\": \"Paralympic Games\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paralympic_Games\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paralympic_Games\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This partnership will support LA28's ambitious \\\"no-new-permanent-venues\\\" plan, which will retrofit existing structures and create temporary venues.\", \"from\": 556, \"to\": 703, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The endeavor, which will cost over $1bn, will transform more than 40 venues across the Los Angeles Metropolitan Area using Autodesk's software tools.\", \"from\": 704, \"to\": 853, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 791, \"end\": 820, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Greater_Los_Angeles\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Los Angeles Metropolitan Area\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Greater_Los_Angeles\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Greater_Los_Angeles\"}, {\"begin\": 827, \"end\": 835, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Autodesk\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.40859526228561e-16, \"text\": \"Autodesk\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Autodesk\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Autodesk\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Autodesk's technology, including Autodesk Construction Cloud and Building Information Modeling (BIM) tools, will play a crucial role in optimizing the venue development process.\", \"from\": 855, \"to\": 1032, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 855, \"end\": 863, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Autodesk\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.40859526228561e-16, \"text\": \"Autodesk\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Autodesk\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Autodesk\"}, {\"begin\": 888, \"end\": 896, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Autodesk\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.40859526228561e-16, \"text\": \"Autodesk\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Autodesk\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Autodesk\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"These tools are expected to streamline project timelines, reduce costs and lower carbon emissions by minimizing the need for new construction materials and energy.\", \"from\": 1033, \"to\": 1196, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Modifying existing buildings aligns with LA28's commitment to sustainability, as built environments account for 42% of global carbon emissions, according to non-profit research organization Architecture 2030.\", \"from\": 1200, \"to\": 1408, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Autodesk's software is a part of our LA28 story: the behind-the-scenes technology that brings our vision of the LA28 Games to life,\\\" LA28 chairperson Casey Wasserman said.\", \"from\": 1410, \"to\": 1582, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1411, \"end\": 1419, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Autodesk\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.40859526228561e-16, \"text\": \"Autodesk\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Autodesk\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Autodesk\"}, {\"begin\": 1561, \"end\": 1576, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Casey_Wasserman\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Casey Wasserman\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Casey_Wasserman\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Casey_Wasserman\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Together, we will develop the right plan to support 12-15 million ticketed fans over such a short period of time.\", \"from\": 1583, \"to\": 1697, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"We are honored to have Autodesk on board for the next four years as we embark on our shared commitment in innovative design that can serve as a precedent for many Games to come.\\\"\", \"from\": 1698, \"to\": 1876, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1721, \"end\": 1729, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Autodesk\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.40859526228561e-16, \"text\": \"Autodesk\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Autodesk\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Autodesk\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The partnership will also aid in designing essential transportation and traffic control elements, which further enhances LA28's resolve for sustainable, effective event planning.\", \"from\": 1880, \"to\": 2058, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Autodesk's technology is used every day to design and make a better world, which is why we are thrilled to be LA28's official Design and Make Platform,\\\" added Andrew Anagnost, Autodesk president and CEO.\", \"from\": 2060, \"to\": 2264, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2061, \"end\": 2069, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Autodesk\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.40859526228561e-16, \"text\": \"Autodesk\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Autodesk\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Autodesk\"}, {\"begin\": 2220, \"end\": 2235, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andrew_Anagnost\", \"score\": 0.9999414210774878, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Andrew Anagnost\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andrew_Anagnost\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andrew_Anagnost\"}, {\"begin\": 2237, \"end\": 2245, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Autodesk\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.40859526228561e-16, \"text\": \"Autodesk\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Autodesk\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Autodesk\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Our partnership will enable Autodesk software to do more than ever before.\", \"from\": 2265, \"to\": 2340, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2294, \"end\": 2302, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Autodesk\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.40859526228561e-16, \"text\": \"Autodesk\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Autodesk\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Autodesk\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Together with LA28, we will help prepare Los Angeles for not only a 29-day celebration but also strengthen the greater Los Angeles community by embarking on our shared vision of a more sustainable Games.\\\"\", \"from\": 2341, \"to\": 2545, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2382, \"end\": 2393, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\", \"score\": 0.9999999410297296, \"rank\": 5.379534885379965e-08, \"text\": \"Los Angeles\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\"}, {\"begin\": 2460, \"end\": 2471, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\", \"score\": 0.9999999410297296, \"rank\": 5.379534885379965e-08, \"text\": \"Los Angeles\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Autodesk has a growing track record of assisting in globally significant projects, includingthe restoration of Notre-Dame de Paris.\", \"from\": 2547, \"to\": 2678, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2547, \"end\": 2555, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Autodesk\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.40859526228561e-16, \"text\": \"Autodesk\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Autodesk\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Autodesk\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Following the cathedral's devastating fire in April 2019, Autodesk's BIM software created a detailed 3D model of the historic structure during its reconstruction.\", \"from\": 2679, \"to\": 2841, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2737, \"end\": 2745, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Autodesk\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.40859526228561e-16, \"text\": \"Autodesk\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Autodesk\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Autodesk\"}, {\"begin\": 2748, \"end\": 2751, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Building_information_modeling\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.651684369512798e-28, \"text\": \"BIM\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Building_information_modeling\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Building_information_modeling\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"For more,sign up for The Drum's daily newsletter here.\", \"from\": 2843, \"to\": 2897, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Autodesk  Autodesk is changing how the world is designed and made.\", \"from\": 2899, \"to\": 2965, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2899, \"end\": 2907, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Autodesk\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.40859526228561e-16, \"text\": \"Autodesk\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Autodesk\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Autodesk\"}, {\"begin\": 2909, \"end\": 2917, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Autodesk\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.40859526228561e-16, \"text\": \"Autodesk\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Autodesk\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Autodesk\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Our technology spans architecture, engineering, construction, product design, manufacturing, and media...  Advertisement\", \"from\": 2968, \"to\": 3088, \"entities\": []}]}"